[S] Sensitive ‚Äî Handle with care
[T] Time-sensitive ‚Äî May expire
[M] Meta ‚Äî About the process itself
[H] Home ‚Äî Anchor point for navigation
Section 9.2 ‚Äî Emoji Quick-Tags
For quick scanning:
